ith ends up in a heated argument with Sujo and Jazla.\n|-\n| 26\n| Bigg Boss warns Sujo and Rajith\n| {{Start date|2020|01|30}}\n| Jazla seems to be getting on everyone's nerves and Veena is the chosen one today. While top three would fight for captaincy, the jail opens up for the worst performers.\n|-\n| 27\n| Rajith Kumar is the new captain\n| {{Start date|2020|01|31}}\n| It's conflict cooking up in the kitchen for Rajith has some qualms about water. As he along with Arya and Jazla compete for captaincy, he nails the task and wins the title.\n|-\n| 28\n| Thesni Khan gets evicted; admits to not being a competitive contestant\n| {{Start date|2020|02|01}}\n| It's that time of the week! Amid a fun task and taking Jazla and Daya to task, Mohanlal announces the result of this week's eviction.\n|-\n| 29\n| Sooraj and Pavan enter the house\n| {{Start date|2020|02|02}}\n| Mohanlal is meeting the evicted contestant, two handsome hunks make their way into the house.\n|-\n| 30\n| Arya becomes the most 'deserving' contestant\n| {{Start date|2020|02|03}}\n| The toughest decision in this game, nominations! While a few of the housemates face the heat, a task to prove how deserving are they leaves the house in splits.\n|-\n| 31\n| Rajith and Reshma lock horns during task\n| {{Start date|2020|02|04}}\n| With the luxury budget task at hand, the housemates are on a roll and the house on fire! Amid decisions and arguments, the drama is at an all time high.<ref>{{cite news|title=The new task creates a ruckus in the house|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-update-february-4-the-new-task-creates-a-ruckus-in-the-house/articleshow/73952920.cms|work=indiatimes.com}}</ref>\n|-\n| 32\n| Bigg Boss house turns into a battlefield\n| {{Start date|2020|02|05}}\n| The housemates get all riled up as the luxury budget task continues.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bigg Boss house turns into a battlefield|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/big