 Surprise</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|09|29}}\n| Bigg Boss gives a grand surprise to the housemates leaving them awestruck.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bigg Boss house welcomes the former contestants|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-day-97-live-update-ex-contestants-to-make-a-surprise-visit/liveblog/66009196.cms}}</ref>\n|-\n| <center>99</center>\n| <center>The Grand Finale Is Here</center>\n| {{Start date|2018|09|30}}\n| The finale promises flashy lights, rocking performances and loads of entertainment. There is excitement in the air as Mohanlal discloses the name of the winner.<ref>{{cite news|title=Sabumon is the winner of Mohanlal\u2019s show|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/television/bigg-boss-malayalam-finale-live-updates-5380336/|work=indianexpress.com}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Season 2 (2020) ===\n{{main|Bigg Boss (Malayalam season 2)}}\nThe second season premiered on 5 January 2019. [[Mohanlal]] returned as the host. The house was built at [[Chennai]], where 17 contestants entered on day-1.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" cellpadding=\"6\" style=\"text-align:center;\n|-\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| {{abbr|Ep. No.|Episode Number}}\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Title\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Original airing\n! style=\"background:#8FBC8F; color:#FFFFFF;| Short summary\n|-\n| <center>1</center>\n| <center>The Grand Launch</center>\n| {{Start date|2020|01|05}}\n| The brand new season of ''Bigg Boss'' is here! Superstar Mohanlal welcomes seventeen new housemates, who are eager to begin their journey in the Bigg Boss ouse. Watch the legend get the ball rolling, however, with a twist in the tale.<ref>{{cite news|title=Bigg Boss Malayalam Season 2 Launch Highlights: The grand reality show witnessed the entry of 17 contestants|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/tv/news/malayalam/bigg-boss-malayalam-2-launch-live-updates-the-reality-show-is-all-set-to-start/li